title: How to write generic types in typescript (+ utility types and more)

media:group.media:title: How to write generic types in typescript (+ utility types and more)
media:group.media:description:
This is the second video of our Typescript series. In this one, we looked at generics and utility types, as well as an example on how to use them with interfaces.

If you haven't seen the previous video, have a look at https://youtu.be/MhYNyfgrCjg
